{"tid":415802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛忍唔住駡個執紙皮既阿婆做屎忽鬼","createTime":"2017-09-27T09:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:21:00.000Z","uid":49163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"194505c08e8fc62554797003fdc9d7179ea8bdb8","tid":415802,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"剛剛係車水馬龍既深水步逛街見到個阿婆<br />\n<br />\n執緊紙皮，我見佢七老八十都要辛苦就起<br />\n<br />\n左側隱之心咁岩口袋有6蚊<br />\n<br />\n我就同佢講你唔洗執喇我用6蚊買起你d紙<br />\n<br />\n皮啦買個包食下，佢就多謝前多謝後笑住<br />\n<br />\n走。<br />\n<br />\n點知我吃完個tea見到佢拎左岩岩我買d紙<br />\n<br />\n皮去賣個刻我真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行個去忍唔住<br />\n<br />\n駡佢正一屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知佢眼紅紅我有<br />\n<br />\n少少後悔就算喇無為同個阿婆計較<br />\n<br />\n我係度諗我究竟有無做錯到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a956d5f7c716f02db1a2023d85dbb36b5cfab04","tid":415802,"uid":33037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"沒有一個廢老是無辜的"},{"pid":"8d77a7eb1a2c387a6acaeefd35c6415a3c20edb7","tid":415802,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒有一個廢老是無辜的</blockquote><br />\n生活咁差佢地都唔想既"},{"pid":"f53ff6094800b60c70bff87aa944fd068b7c68b2","tid":415802,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"睇你個名就知你假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edbec4e76de4e63ba95b403e5c793dc2d0d4dce","tid":415802,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"你買完啲紙樣皮打算點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb238fc0241de8a3ba9f014f4539e0d5a2cea84","tid":415802,"uid":479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"你唔撚洗 大吹大擂又話係邊個個仔 正屎忽鬼～"},{"pid":"6b9c1db41cd9d0ab67d4f3159893ffe2e49ae3a1","tid":415802,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"阿婆我對你唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf2a2d9da74c7d97468c72ba1e6f94a565fc985","tid":415802,"uid":119605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人唔明樓主講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e940dbb6a206a6e7ef1f7d2778d2f0ad5923ad","tid":415802,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人唔明樓主講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係唔識字麻"},{"pid":"471ad13c01c7a5603b5b0519b06315e4c837ca17","tid":415802,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"樓主應該諗住會有人用佢個名黎鬧佢"},{"pid":"d8ad169d7d6948f327d8c3b48b6372a20b0e240c","tid":415802,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主應該諗住會有人用佢個名黎鬧佢</blockquote><br />\n典解無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}